{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_52_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 優のおすすめスポット",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、こんな所でどうしたんだ？　瑠依\nてっきり観光に出かけたと思っていたんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? What are you doing here‚ Rui?\nI thought you’d already gone sightseeing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.010476017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……こ、こんな所で奇遇ですね\n……あれ？　今まで外に行っていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… wh-what a coincidence‚ meeting you here.\n…Wait‚ were you out somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8464621862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、沙季の観光に付き合っていたんだ\n一段落ついたから、一旦旅館に戻って来たところだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I was accompanying Saki on her sightseeing.\nWe wrapped up for now‚ so I came back to the inn for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか、沙季と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… with Saki‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4578677814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依は、今から観光か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you heading out for sightseeing now‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5632191896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5632191896
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.8809290249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです！\n行きたい場所にはこれから向かう予定で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that’s right!\nI’m just about to go to a place I’ve been wanting to visit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "優のおすすめスポットに行く予定なんですけど\n一人で行くにはロマンチックな場所で、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a spot Yu recommended.\nBut‚ um… it’s a bit too romantic to go alone‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.7149186928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、それは良かった\n優が京都に詳しくて助かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ sounds nice.\nIt’s great that Yu knows Kyoto so well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そ、そうですね。優には頭が上がりません\nそれで、その、{user}さんも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Y-Yes‚ exactly. I really owe Yu a lot.\nSo‚ um… {user}-san‚ would you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.6167107105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、移動したいのか\nそれならタクシーでも呼ぼうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you want to head out now?\nThen shall I call a taxi for you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "タクシーならもう呼びました！\nそ、それで……一緒に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I already called one!\nA-and… would you come with…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.8348969777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、じゃあもう出るんだな\n今日はゆっくり羽根を伸ばしてきてくれ、瑠依",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So you’re heading out now.\nTake it easy and enjoy yourself today‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.4868243535
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……もう！　そうじゃなくて！\nタクシー移動なら一人も二人も変わりませんよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Argh! That’s not what I meant!\nIt’s a taxi—doesn’t make a difference if it’s one or two people‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0936980248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "優の紹介してくれた場所は一人だとちょっと\n行き辛い場所で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The place Yu recommended is kind of hard\nto go to alone… you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.645078248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか……なら、一緒に来てる誰かを\n誘って行けばいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… then wouldn’t that be better for you\nto ask someone else who came with you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.2879575093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "みんなもそれぞれ自分の予定を入れてます\nそれにほら、タクシーも到着しましたし、乗らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone already has their own plans.\nAnd look‚ the taxi’s here already—we should get in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5247608414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ちょ、瑠依？　なんで俺の腕を引っ張る？\nせっかくの慰安旅行なのに、俺が同伴でいいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? W-wait‚ Rui? Why are you pulling my arm?\nThis is a recreational trip‚ are you sure you want me tagging along?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2639.978790300006,
          "startTime": 103.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1439.9787903000033,
          "startTime": 102.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "私を助けると思って、さぁ、行きましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think of it as helping me—come on‚ let’s go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0252396267,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
