    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 115.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ここが優おすすめの神社か……\n「縁結びにご利益がある」って書いてあるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is the shrine Yu recommended…\nIt says here it’s blessed for good relationships.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "紅葉や花が植えられていて、綺麗な神社ですね\nそれに、人で凄く賑わってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The maple leaves and flowers make it such a beautiful shrine.\nAnd it’s so lively with people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.478135168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.8567144078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが来てくれて良かったです\n一人だったら尻込みしちゃってたかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really glad you came with me‚ {user}-san.\nI might’ve chickened out if I’d come alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、凄い人だかりだもんな\n……ところで、なんだか男女の二人組が多くないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True‚ it’s really crowded here.\n…By the way‚ aren’t there a lot of couples here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.3178251905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
